Background & Scope of the Crisis

According to WHO‚Äôs ‚ÄúWorld Mental Health Today‚Äù and ‚ÄúMental Health Atlas 2024‚Äù reports:

The figure of ‚Äúover one billion people‚Äù includes those with diagnosed mental disorders and also broader ‚Äúmental health conditions‚Äù ‚Äî including distress, impairment in functioning, or risk of self-harm. 
PMC
